ong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣洗地</span></strong></span>開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74f3ee3d24195a698d2ad6b2116e8fbac270b196","tid":1631763,"uid":312125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:16:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>文宣國際線要你幫手</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f626ea594aaf42272e6440d253b73f4823371b7e","tid":1631763,"uid":331388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:16:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf7e745ae6b63a3e4fb1deca4ecb8da1ca612d1c","tid":1631763,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:16:17.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"5c0b8f7259c6332e743fedd9f310b1d1dc4ee042","tid":1631763,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ec1242229d20d37129857278aab424b2e972eda","tid":1631763,"uid":38778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6788fe2fd888bfacf2ea6ad4627f2cb53181390a","tid":1631763,"uid":81149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n已在twitter like &amp; retweet"},{"pid":"7fdff26293482a596631d6c404370cdacdf661d0","tid":1631763,"uid":136590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47061275b787d20b0aa6563fd1af2213e6a82cf","tid":1631763,"uid":66828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b919680af55ff05298d32c5ee654c2553e876c36","tid":1631763,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MzE523y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMzE523y.jpg&h=1a0e2ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zKw4zaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.